{"tid":746755,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國 3D 打印槍械藍圖合法化　開源組織將上載更多槍械藍圖","createTime":"2018-07-17T23:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T04:15:06.000Z","uid":53379,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8334ae0c521ca1d1420dd53a82c2c79934b826c0","tid":746755,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T23:26:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>美國 3D 打印槍械藍圖合法化　開源組織將上載更多槍械藍圖</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n日前美國司法部終止同 3D 打印槍枝的主要開源組織 Defense Distributed 的訴訟，達成和解。美國政府允許該組織利用 3D 打印技術，來製作槍枝藍圖，而不會被警察拘捕。這宗案件的完結，為未來槍械設計與製作的門檻大幅降低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Liberator.3d.gun_.vv_.01-694x463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FLiberator.3d.gun_.vv_.01-694x463.jpg&h=ddaf9814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/liberator_1-694x477.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fliberator_1-694x477.png&h=ba73b3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國民可合法擁有槍械，但在網路上發佈槍械的製造圖，並任由人下載，以 3D 打印槍械是否合法，一直成為當地爭論的話題。而美國司法部因此同開源組織 Defense Distributed 展開長達 3 年的訴訟。在 2013 年，該組織的創辦人 Cody Wilson 在網路上發表第一支由 3D 打印塑膠手槍「Liberator」。這支手槍由 16 個部件所組成。但當時美國政府以違反《國際武器貿易便例》要求他把槍支與公開的設計藍圖下架。Cody Wilson 為此向美國政府提告，指他發佈 3D 打印槍械的行為，受到美國憲法第一修正案保障國民言論自由、第二修正案擁有槍械自由的保護。<br />\n<br />\n3D 打印槍械的爭論點是，世界上任何人，包括犯罪份子，都有可能在家中製作毫無標記、無法追縱的槍枝。槍械設計圖在互聯網上自由傳播，而且能夠實際製作出來。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Defense Distributed 的網站已經重開。另一方面，他們正使用圖中的光學測量儀，為現時市面上多種槍械製作 3D 打印藍圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Cody-Wilson-02w-694x521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FCody-Wilson-02w-694x521.jpg&h=667f403d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/DD-05w-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FDD-05w-694x390.jpg&h=b32f6708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/DD-01w-1-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FDD-01w-1-694x390.jpg&h=4e9e1316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：TechCrunch, Wired<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/15/3dprintgun/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F3dprintgun%2Flife-tech%2F&d=tOLpo1X6ylTatJXlymuDVuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=cbf89792\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/15/3dprintgun/life-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7d5a3e8213ba31aa8b396496d1dfa66971a914","tid":746755,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T23:40:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線真係殺咗人都搵唔到兇手架喎呢啲膠槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c25a927f65bc949141e2b00122d461a6aeb4f6","tid":746755,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"2f7d5a3e8213ba31aa8b396496d1dfa66971a914","tid":746755,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T23:40:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線真係殺咗人都搵唔到兇手架喎呢啲膠槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T23:43:06.000Z","msg":"你估真係人人都有部咁嘅3D printer咩"},{"pid":"fffa70e7592edca7814e179395316feeec4e344a","tid":746755,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f7d5a3e8213ba31aa8b396496d1dfa66971a914","tid":746755,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T23:40:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線真係殺咗人都搵唔到兇手架喎呢啲膠槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy